com.foreach.across.modules.entity.bind

Interface EntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface EntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver
    Responsible for resolving the value that should be used for a template of a particular property. A template is usually represented by either ListEntityPropertyBinder.getItemTemplate() or MapEntityPropertyBinder.getTemplate().

    The value is mostly used for pre-filling controls.

    Since:
    3.3.0
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
